      "id": "5a93c517_1630009d",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/clamp/charts/mariadb/templates/pv.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 36,
      "message": "I have to disagree on this.\nUsing Release.Name creates many directories under /dockerdata-nfs, making it impossible to distinguish data between different deployments of onap on same k8s. Therefore the only option to have multiple deployments of onap on same k8s is to use .Release.Namespace\nAlso, it looks much cleaner.\nWe agreed that currently using --namespace in helm install is mandatory.",
